mobile-frontend-editor-editing-page:
A heading saying what page is being edited. All text should be wrapped in a STRONG tag except the page title itself. Note that STRONG text pushes the buttons off-screen when it's too long (vertical mobile display), but the SPAN part is shortened in that case with an ellipsis (...) before the buttons.

Parameters:
* $1 - page title
{{Related|Mobile-frontend-editor-page}}
{{Identical|Editing}}

